lains and challenges neoliberal policies, Neoliberalism and Everyday Life is an important assessment of a political system that makes profit easier and people's lives more difficult.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 7aPOLITICAL SCIENCE / General.2bisacsh1 aArmstrong, Pat, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBezanson², Kate, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBraedley, Susan, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aConnell, Raewyn, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCôté-Boucher, Karine, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLuxton, Meg, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aLuxton, Meg, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPinto, Paula C., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aThomas, Mark, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Complete eBook-Package 2011-2010z978311127414008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Upgrade eBook-Package 2011 - 2010z978311127721940uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978077358105040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780773581050423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780773581050/original  a978-3-11-127414-0  ACUP Complete eBook-Package 2011-2010c2010d2011  a978-3-11-127721-9  ACUP Upgrade eBook-Package 2011 - 2010c2010d2011  aGBV-deGruyter-alles